ZH: 我完全赞同他的观点。
EN: I totally agree with his point of view.

ZH: 我们应该赞同他的决定。
EN: We should support his decision.

ZH: 我赞同你的看法。
EN: I agree with your opinion.

ZH: 她赞同我的做法。
EN: She approves of my actions.

ZH: 请你为我的计划提供赞同。
EN: Please give your endorsement for my plan.

ZH: 我们必须赞同这个倡议。
EN: We must approve of this initiative.

ZH: 这是一项我无法赞同的提案。
EN: This is a proposal I cannot agree with.

ZH: 我们必须听从上级的赞同。
EN: We must obey the superior's approval.

ZH: 他的建议得到了平级管理者的赞同。
EN: His suggestion received approval from peers.

ZH: 如果你赞同，请举手。
EN: If you agree, please raise your hand.

ZH: 我完全赞同这个观点。
EN: I fully endorse this viewpoint.

ZH: 我们不能赞同这种不公正的决定。
EN: We cannot condone this unfair decision.

ZH: 他对这个提案提出了赞同。
EN: He expressed his agreement with the proposal.

ZH: 我已经得到老板的赞同了。
EN: I have obtained the boss's approval.

ZH: 老师不会赞同我们的懒散。
EN: The teacher will not approve of our laziness.

ZH: 我们赞同你的选择。
EN: We support your choice.

ZH: 这个计划得到了大家的赞同。
EN: This plan has received everyone's agreement.

ZH: 她的说法得到了学生们的赞同。
EN: Her statement has gained the students' endorsement.

ZH: 我们赞同他的解决方案。
EN: We concur with his proposed solution.

ZH: 别人的意见赞同不赞同都无所谓，就是要自己开心。
EN: It doesn't matter if others agree or not, what matters is that you are happy.
